{
  "stem": "4760.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I then joined my parents by the other Senamaud family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- that was over-- over a barn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had to stay three people in one room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Europe, you did not have toilet facility.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All you had is a little [LAUGHS] pot in the middle of the-- of the room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you had to do your business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And naturally, my mother is a woman, and she-- you know, she put a curtain around her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was laying here in bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- they were laying their in bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't suffer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got three nice meals a day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people were just wonderful to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then in [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] April-- no, in November of '42, we were supposed to go to Switzerland, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some relative of ours made connection to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the day we were supposed to leave, that was cancelled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I had to go back to my parents, again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because, through-- through our uncle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through our uncle and grandparents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- you know, they-- then-- then finally a friend of ours, who-- who was actually my grandma's maid, they lived in southern part of France near Lourdes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've heard about the city of Lourdes, where they heal all the people and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near Spain, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came up to Limoges and told us that quite a few people now were crossing the border from France to Spain, and then go to the French consul.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they can join the French Army or whatever, the-- the underground, again, in Morocco.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So naturally, we-- we were getting restless, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, can't be cooped up at 12, 14-- with 16, 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
